The paper deals with emotion recognition from facial expressions, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also addresses the issue of incomplete labels, which is a problem in human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and multimodal learning (cs.MM). Finally, the paper proposes a novel algorithm for multitask learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
